# Generated stubs for scaffolded-but-not-yet-implemented clients are not committed
# yet — buf.gen.yaml is verified in CI as a smoke test instead. Once a language's
# wrapper layer is implemented (see README status table), remove its entry here
# and commit the generated output, matching go/gen.
python/src/signet/
python/src/admin/
rust/src/gen/
rust/target/
# Library crate — consumers resolve their own dependency tree; regenerated
# fresh by CI on every run.
rust/Cargo.lock
csharp/gen/
csharp/bin/
csharp/obj/
# TypeScript: src/gen is committed (matching go/gen) now that the wrapper
# layer is implemented. dist/ (build output) and node_modules/ (installed
# dependencies) are never generated-schema-stub content, so they stay
# ignored permanently regardless of implementation status.
typescript/dist/
typescript/node_modules/
csharp/SignetClient.Tests/bin/
csharp/SignetClient.Tests/obj/
